00:37:09,584 --> 00:37:14,594
right, so have it in the night.

253
00:37:14,594 --> 00:37:21,594
In every small thing you will see. Some people
were coming from India and they had to bring

254
00:37:21,894 --> 00:37:28,894
My two boxes from there and they wouldn't
allow these boxes, they said it is overweight,

255
00:37:29,073 --> 00:37:33,344
overweight. So they didn't know what to do.
They thought that they should send them back

