00:37:49,334 --> 00:38:01,439
drama; and then they were put into some sort
of a tourist hotel for that night. Next morning

259
00:38:01,464 --> 00:38:16,105
they met two other Indians from, sahaja yogis,
from Poona, two boys. That settled it! My

260
00:38:16,144 --> 00:38:24,008
luggage, they could put it in their name and
that’s how the luggage came in. But they

261
00:38:24,033 --> 00:38:31,033
never felt bored: 19 hours. “We had nice
time, Mother, together. We were enjoying and

262
00:38:31,303 --> 00:38:37,174
talking,” finished! Nobody feels the time
