00:38:48,958 --> 00:38:52,484
for 19hours, “My God, what is this!!”
Would have given it in the newspapers. Everybody

265
00:38:52,703 --> 00:38:59,334
… this is the greatest crime! While these
were enjoying life nicely.

266
00:39:01,008 --> 00:39:09,903
So, we have lost now the sense of aim. We
don't have any aims. We just want to enjoy.

267
00:39:12,641 --> 00:39:20,809
It’s a very, very big thing that has happened
because, as you know, the joy in the Sahastrara

268
00:39:20,834 --> 00:39:33,899
is nira-ananda, nira-ananda. Of course, Nira
is My name also, but it means pure absolute

269
00:39:33,924 --> 00:39:47,689
joy. Nira-ananda. And that nirananda, that
joy has no other hues. It’s just pure, pure

270
00:39:47,714 --> 00:39:56,909
joy. Without thinking, it just pours into
it. After all, every activity is for what,

271
00:39:56,934 --> 00:40:04,707
for getting some sort of a pleasure, sensation
and also, some people believe, for joy. It’s

272
00:40:04,732 --> 00:40:05,604
not.

273
00:40:05,909 --> 00:40:11,324
Only after the opening of Sahastrara and the
cleansing of it, then you will know what is

274
00:40:11,349 --> 00:40:12,199
joy.

275
00:40:12,405 --> 00:40:18,893
You can't explain it, how you can spend hours
together like this. People don't understand.

276
00:40:19,418 --> 00:40:23,674
Like even our mayor was telling Me that, “We
can't sit in the church for more than fifteen

277
00:40:23,674 --> 00:40:31,849
minutes. And how people are sitting here for
