285
00:41:22,964 --> 00:41:29,964
This is the most important thing in life,
which you can have only through Sahaja Yoga,

286
00:41:30,553 --> 00:41:36,424
because your Sahastraras are open, because
they are opened out.

287
00:41:36,424 --> 00:41:44,594
There is now one more thing I have to tell
you, that is very important for all of you

288
00:41:44,619 --> 00:41:56,696
to remember: that, while living in this Ocean
