00:42:41,074 --> 00:42:48,569
Sahaja Yoga. So is very important for all
of you to know that you have got the light

295
00:42:48,594 --> 00:42:55,334
to be given to others. Come forward. Don't
have fear of your ego, conditionings, nothing.

296
00:42:55,334 --> 00:43:01,763
Come forward. You have all the strength, you
have everything within yourself and you will

297
00:43:01,763 --> 00:43:08,344
do everything with such happiness and joy.
Everywhere, in every country people are doing

298
00:43:08,344 --> 00:43:13,384
that, but some of them are doing, some of
them are not doing. All of you are quite capable

299
00:43:13,384 --> 00:43:22,515
of doing it, so please come forward and see
for yourself what you are capable of.

300
00:43:23,214 --> 00:43:29,904
First of all you should have faith in yourself.
If you have no faith in yourself, you cannot

301
00:43:31,706 --> 00:43:41,887
do anything. Have faith. You should have no
fears of any kind. And also to introspect,

302
00:43:41,912 --> 00:43:52,122
to see within yourself what's going on. To
