305
00:44:08,364 --> 00:44:14,324
It’s very remarkable, as you have seen,
that from the candle you get cool breeze.

306
00:44:14,349 --> 00:44:20,504
How you can get it from the candle, cool breeze?
You do get.

307
00:44:20,813 --> 00:44:34,294
So, is important to recognise yourself as
a Sahaja yogi and to recognise - what have

308
00:44:34,319 --> 00:44:42,806
you done for Sahaja Yoga? Without doing for
