315
00:45:20,434 --> 00:45:28,434
Yoga? What have we done for Sahaja Yoga? After
some time, you will do a lot and you will

316
00:45:28,504 --> 00:45:34,543
never know you have done anything for Sahaja
Yoga. Very surprising, it happens to so many

317
00:45:34,543 --> 00:45:44,069
of you and should happen to all of you. I
